        <abstract> 
<p>Agrees that new book [<hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>] be published on old terms. Hopes it will not fail.</p> 
            <p>CD is curious to read an essay on evolution by a Hindu, which is being sent to Murray from India.</p>
